<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Aug1928"><font color="red">12 August 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Lucia Joyce): He himself has trouble with his eyes, but the doctor hopes it is a superficial attack. He has had to stop work which he had begun </div>
